---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Logipop - ロジカルシンキング力向上プラットフォーム">
	<section class="py-20 px-4">
		<div class="container mx-auto text-center">
			<h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6">
				論理的思考力を<br />
				<span class="text-primary">向上させよう</span>
			</h1>
			<p class="text-xl text-muted-foreground mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
				Logipopは、体系的なトレーニングでロジカルシンキング力を鍛えるプラットフォームです。
				実践的な問題解決能力を身につけましょう。
			</p>
			<div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
				<a 
					href="/app" 
					class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md text-sm font-medium transition-colors focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-1 focus-visible:ring-ring bg-primary text-primary-foreground shadow hover:bg-primary/90 h-11 px-8"
				>
					今すぐ始める
				</a>
				<a 
					href="/features" 
					class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md text-sm font-medium transition-colors focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-1 focus-visible:ring-ring border border-input bg-background shadow-sm hover:bg-accent hover:text-accent-foreground h-11 px-8"
				>
					機能を見る
				</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="py-20 px-4 bg-muted/30">
		<div class="container mx-auto">
			<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">主な機能</h2>
			<div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
				<div class="text-center p-6 rounded-lg bg-background shadow-sm">
					<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
						<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
						</svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">体系的なトレーニング</h3>
					<p class="text-muted-foreground">段階的に難易度を上げながら、論理的思考力を着実に向上させます。</p>
				</div>
				
				<div class="text-center p-6 rounded-lg bg-background shadow-sm">
					<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
						<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
						</svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">実践的な問題</h3>
					<p class="text-muted-foreground">ビジネスシーンで活用できる実践的な論理思考問題を提供します。</p>
				</div>
				
				<div class="text-center p-6 rounded-lg bg-background shadow-sm">
					<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
						<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z" />
						</svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">進捗管理</h3>
					<p class="text-muted-foreground">学習の進捗を可視化し、継続的な成長をサポートします。</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="py-20 px-4">
		<div class="container mx-auto text-center">
			<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">今すぐ始めましょう</h2>
			<p class="text-xl text-muted-foreground mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
				論理的思考力の向上は一朝一夕では身につきません。<br />
				継続的なトレーニングで着実にスキルアップしましょう。
			</p>
			<a 
				href="/app" 
				class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md text-sm font-medium transition-colors focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-1 focus-visible:ring-ring bg-primary text-primary-foreground shadow hover:bg-primary/90 h-11 px-8"
			>
				無料で始める
			</a>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>